OL,5,G1030 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FKeighly and Justin host at The
OL,7,     FHalf Moon Inn, in Norfolk.
OL,8,     FJustin's been talking up his chef
OL,9,     Fcredentials all week. But he
OL,10,     Fshould be wary of the B&Ber's
OL,11,     Fbiggest foe: the poached egg.
OL,12,G1100 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FToilet troubles, tossing and
OL,14,     Fturning, and tears galore. It's a
OL,15,     Frip-roaring payment day on Four in
OL,16,     Fa Bed. But who's won the week?
OL,17,G1130 Four in a Bed
